message: Rule applicable: mod_to_bubble ([("Bubble", 6000)]), to expression: b % c, resulting in: {SafeMod(b,c) @ (c != 0)}
Rule applicable: bubble_up ([("Bubble", 8900)]), to expression: (a != {SafeMod(b,c) @ (c != 0)}), resulting in: {(a != SafeMod(b,c)) @ And([(c != 0)])}
Rule applicable: expand_bubble ([("Bubble", 8900)]), to expression: {(a != SafeMod(b,c)) @ And([(c != 0)])}, resulting in: And([(a != SafeMod(b,c)), And([(c != 0)])])
Rule applicable: flatten_binop ([("Minion", 4400)]), to expression: (a != SafeMod(b,c)), resulting in: (a != __0)
Rule applicable: remove_unit_vector_and ([("Base", 8800)]), to expression: And([(c != 0)]), resulting in: (c != 0)
Rule applicable: introduce_modeq ([("Minion", 4200)]), to expression: __0 =aux SafeMod(b,c), resulting in: ModEq(b, c, __0)
